Test the Rest APIs through the postman:

A. Register Tourist

Method: POST

URL: http://localhost:6990/app/tourist/registration

Requestbody:

{

    "name": "Ronaldo",

    "gender": "Male",

    "age": 25,

    "fromPlace": "New York",

    "numberOfDaysVisits": 7,

    "createdDate": "2024-08-01T00:00:00Z"

}

Response:

{

    "touristId": 1,

    "name": "Ronaldo",

    "gender": "Male",

    "age": 25,

    "fromPlace": "New York",

    "numberOfDaysVisits": 7,

    "createdDate": "2024-08-01T00:00:00Z"

}

B. Update Tourist

Method: PUT

URL: http://localhost:6990/app/tourist/update

Requestbody:

{

    "touristId": 1,

    "name": "Ronaldo",

    "gender": "Male",

    "age": 26,

    "fromPlace": "New York",

    "numberOfDaysVisits": 10,

    "createdDate": "2024-08-01T00:00:00Z"

}

Response:

"Updated Successfully"

C. Find Tourist by Name

Method: GET

URL: http://localhost:6990/app/tourist/get-tourist-list-by-name?name=Ronaldo

Response:

[

    {

        "touristId": 1,

        "name": "Ronaldo",

        "gender": "Male",

        "age": 26,

        "fromPlace": "New York",

        "numberOfDaysVisits": 10,

        "createdDate": "2024-08-01T00:00:00Z"

    }

]

E. Delete Tourist by ID

Method: DELETE

URL: http://localhost:6990/app/tourist/delete-tourist-by-id?id=1

Response:

"Deleted Successfully"